snippet.title: Johnny Depp wrote on walls in blood UK court hears
snippet.description:
The third day of Johnny Depp's libel case against UK tabloid newspaper The Sun has been hearing how he wrote on walls in blood and suffered "some species of a nervous breakdown" during a violent argument with his ex-wife and fellow actress Amber Heard.
